description:
Kaga, as an Abyssal Vessel.
The night before the battle of Ironbottom Sound, http://anidb.net/ch65838 [Kaga] revealed that she was sunk once and became Abyssal Vessel shortly after that. Her memories of the time when she was Abyssal Vessel still remained even after she was sunk for the second time, but as a Abyssal Vessel instead, just to be recreated into Fleet Girl again.
name: Kaga
